WEBVTT

00:13.000 --> 00:15.440
[Palace of Eternal Peace]

00:14.240 --> 00:15.100
Your Highness,

00:15.270 --> 00:17.350
the peach blossom pastry
and preserved fruits

00:17.350 --> 00:19.000
you ordered for Lady Xie have arrived.

00:19.000 --> 00:20.060
Please have a taste

00:20.320 --> 00:21.440
and see which one

00:21.440 --> 00:22.920
agrees with Lady Xie best.

00:25.960 --> 00:26.760
Who made this?

00:30.760 --> 00:31.760
Lift up your head.

00:34.960 --> 00:35.710
It's you?

00:35.840 --> 00:37.770
Your Highness still remembers me.

00:38.280 --> 00:39.380
Take the others away.

00:39.380 --> 00:40.840
Everyone, leave the room.

00:44.640 --> 00:46.320
How do you know how to make hawthorn cake?

00:46.320 --> 00:47.780
Before entering the palace,

00:47.780 --> 00:50.310
I had a long stay
at Prince Jing'an's Mansion.

00:50.750 --> 00:52.810
I often heard the servants talk about

00:53.070 --> 00:55.430
Lady Xie making hawthorn cake
for Your Highness.

00:55.430 --> 00:57.680
So I tried my hand at making some
using her method.

00:57.680 --> 00:59.410
Did anyone allow you to do that?

00:59.710 --> 01:02.070
Now, I get mad
at the sight of hawthorn cake,

01:02.070 --> 01:03.150
for it always reminds me

01:03.150 --> 01:04.950
of who my beloved Yaoyao is with.

01:06.790 --> 01:07.320
Get out!

01:08.510 --> 01:09.000
Yes.

02:37.130 --> 02:40.990
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

02:41.079 --> 02:43.920
[Episode 16]

02:46.430 --> 02:47.430
Mother, it hurts.

02:47.680 --> 02:48.880
Do be gentle, Mother.

02:48.910 --> 02:49.640
Drop the act.

02:52.360 --> 02:53.910
It does hurt a little.

02:54.470 --> 02:57.079
You used to dream of traveling
far and wide

02:58.240 --> 02:59.640
and exploring the world.

03:00.360 --> 03:01.820
After what just happened,

03:01.960 --> 03:03.490
do you still want to do that?

03:06.000 --> 03:06.630
Mother,

03:07.150 --> 03:08.550
only when I left Jiankang

03:09.190 --> 03:11.450
did I realize what the real world is like.

03:11.870 --> 03:14.120
There aren't fine clothes
and lavish feasts,

03:14.120 --> 03:16.050
nor thousands of dazzling lights.

03:18.470 --> 03:20.800
Take the girl in court today
as an example.

03:20.800 --> 03:22.930
Just like that, she saw her own brother

03:23.120 --> 03:25.120
die a tragic death right before her.

03:25.560 --> 03:26.690
Perhaps she already

03:27.280 --> 03:28.480
lost her only family.

03:30.120 --> 03:31.050
To add to that...

03:32.240 --> 03:35.040
nobody will ever fix a honey drink
for her anymore.

03:36.430 --> 03:38.910
By contrast, some people are utterly vile,

03:39.750 --> 03:40.800
just like Cui Jun.

03:41.360 --> 03:42.430
He even harmed his own little sister

03:42.430 --> 03:44.360
just for the Phoenix Heart Tokens.

03:45.079 --> 03:45.520
Right.

03:47.710 --> 03:50.170
Empress Wenxi and I were
as close as sisters.

03:50.680 --> 03:52.750
She often talked about her older brother

03:52.750 --> 03:54.880
to me, describing him as an upstanding

03:55.360 --> 03:56.630
and ambitious man.

03:57.310 --> 03:59.150
To survey the mineral deposits of Ye,

03:59.150 --> 04:01.010
he travelled to nearly
every part of the country.

04:01.010 --> 04:03.080
But based on what Cui Jun did today,

04:03.880 --> 04:07.080
he is completely different
from what Empress Wenxi said.

04:10.210 --> 04:11.410
I've never seen this.

04:16.950 --> 04:18.079
Then, has there been

04:18.240 --> 04:20.240
anything odd about your father
after he returned

04:20.240 --> 04:21.370
from the northern desert region?

04:21.370 --> 04:22.830
I once heard from my mother

04:23.360 --> 04:24.510
that my father was severely injured

04:24.510 --> 04:25.480
upon his return.

04:25.800 --> 04:26.800
After he recovered,

04:26.800 --> 04:28.510
he became completely different.

04:28.510 --> 04:29.510
He was cold, indifferent,

04:29.510 --> 04:30.640
violent, and harsh,

04:30.680 --> 04:32.810
unlike the loving parent he used to be.

04:33.120 --> 04:35.520
Shortly after that, my mother passed away.

04:35.630 --> 04:36.760
Please think again.

04:37.159 --> 04:38.040
Any other change?

04:38.040 --> 04:39.240
My mother also told me

04:39.430 --> 04:40.690
that my father somehow

04:40.800 --> 04:42.190
became interested in studying

04:42.190 --> 04:44.000
mineral deposits and maps.

04:45.070 --> 04:46.200
Please think again.

04:46.480 --> 04:47.680
What does your father

04:48.310 --> 04:49.310
enjoy eating?

04:49.750 --> 04:51.190
He doesn't like or dislike

04:51.190 --> 04:52.590
anything in particular.

04:53.070 --> 04:54.000
However, in recent years,

04:54.000 --> 04:56.159
I've noticed that my father
no longer enjoys tea.

04:56.159 --> 04:57.870
Instead, he prefers milk

04:58.630 --> 05:00.890
and all sorts of pastries made with milk.

05:19.830 --> 05:20.720
This wheel?

05:21.740 --> 05:22.940
Why does he have this?

05:23.680 --> 05:24.870
Isn't it what I made for Shao Yang

05:24.870 --> 05:26.330
years ago in Northern Qin?

05:28.240 --> 05:29.920
You disappeared for 20 years.

05:32.560 --> 05:33.750
I really thought

05:33.950 --> 05:35.070
you were dead,

05:36.830 --> 05:37.720
Chu Zhu.

05:38.750 --> 05:41.070
Nothing gets past you.

05:44.430 --> 05:45.920
You put on a disguise mask

05:45.920 --> 05:47.720
and began hiding in Southern Ye.

05:47.800 --> 05:50.060
Shao Yang instructed you to do so, right?

05:50.860 --> 05:52.420
This is my master's order

05:54.070 --> 05:55.430
and my mission.

05:57.750 --> 05:59.310
Then what about the real Cui Jun?

05:59.310 --> 06:02.000
Twenty years ago, when he travelled
the northern desert region,

06:02.000 --> 06:05.040
I killed him in an attempt to seize
the map of mineral deposits

06:05.040 --> 06:05.920
drawn by him.

06:06.680 --> 06:09.000
Unfortunately, I was one step too late.

06:09.480 --> 06:11.630
He had already sent the map
back to the Capital.

06:11.630 --> 06:12.630
This map was later

06:12.920 --> 06:14.920
stashed in the Phoenix Heart Tokens

06:14.950 --> 06:16.720
by Empress Wenxi.

06:18.360 --> 06:20.560
Let me ask you. Did you also orchestrate

06:20.630 --> 06:23.240
the wrongful cases
involving the An and Lu families

06:23.240 --> 06:25.170
and causing my clansmen's deaths?

06:26.170 --> 06:28.170
I am a slave bought by Shao Yang.

06:28.240 --> 06:29.560
She is my master.

06:30.190 --> 06:31.560
Whatever she asks me to do,

06:31.560 --> 06:32.820
I will absolutely do it

06:33.190 --> 06:34.920
as long as I'm still breathing,

06:37.510 --> 06:41.110
including eliminating the An
and Lu families and your clansmen,

06:41.900 --> 06:43.380
as she commanded.

06:49.800 --> 06:50.680
Well, well.

06:51.600 --> 06:53.510
Not only did my love betrayed me,

06:56.040 --> 06:58.750
but my best friend
also stabbed me in the back.

07:01.590 --> 07:02.990
Not long ago in Jiankang,

07:04.910 --> 07:06.150
I met Shao Yang.

07:06.630 --> 07:07.890
How is my master doing?

07:08.270 --> 07:09.160
Your master

07:11.160 --> 07:12.270
got seriously ill.

07:13.390 --> 07:16.590
She passed away
shortly after returning to Northern Qin.

07:19.190 --> 07:21.050
Will you continue to work for her?

07:27.200 --> 07:28.460
This is a design of mine

07:28.920 --> 07:30.480
for sealing the imperial mausoleum

07:30.480 --> 07:31.430
with water.

07:31.890 --> 07:32.740
Tell me.

07:32.780 --> 07:34.640
What exactly are you trying to do?

07:34.970 --> 07:36.730
To destroy Lingfeng Fort.

07:37.390 --> 07:39.490
All the iron-contaminated water
in the mine

07:39.490 --> 07:41.810
is sealed under this wheel.

07:42.040 --> 07:43.240
Six hours ago,

07:43.260 --> 07:44.990
I already activated the wheel.

07:45.240 --> 07:48.950
Lingfeng Fort will soon be submerged
by the polluted water.

07:49.140 --> 07:51.950
Everyone will die.

07:56.510 --> 07:57.510
You're crazy.

07:59.500 --> 08:02.830
The wheel mechanism
is full of hidden weapons.

08:03.160 --> 08:04.120
Mulian Ying,

08:04.800 --> 08:06.130
you will definitely not

08:06.820 --> 08:08.090
make it back alive.

08:09.370 --> 08:12.130
All of you will have to die with me!

08:17.680 --> 08:19.600
My mother just made some honey water.

08:19.600 --> 08:20.780
I brought a bowl of it for you.

08:20.780 --> 08:22.110
Drink it when it's warm.

08:24.920 --> 08:26.580
You didn't poison it, did you?

08:27.700 --> 08:28.380
Yes, I did.

08:29.190 --> 08:30.870
I added in stuff like datura,

08:30.870 --> 08:32.789
aconite, and Qianji poison.

08:36.669 --> 08:39.480
Why did you still drink it
when I told you it was poisoned?

08:39.480 --> 08:41.480
Because I wanted to be killed by you.

08:42.080 --> 08:42.740
Is it sweet?

08:48.750 --> 08:50.610
Thank you for saving those girls.

08:51.620 --> 08:53.480
If they decide to hush them for good,

08:53.480 --> 08:54.480
what will happen to these girls?

08:54.480 --> 08:56.030
-Please help us!
-Please help us!

08:56.030 --> 09:00.360
-Help us!
-Help us!

09:00.410 --> 09:02.440
-I beg you!
-Please!

09:02.440 --> 09:04.300
-Please help us!
-Please help us!

09:04.750 --> 09:06.810
Also, thank you for saving my mother.

09:07.000 --> 09:08.870
Does your wound still hurt?

09:09.080 --> 09:11.270
It's normal to get injured in battle.

09:11.510 --> 09:13.240
This wound is barely anything.

09:14.960 --> 09:17.020
My hunch tells me something's wrong.

09:17.720 --> 09:18.780
Is it about Cui Jun?

09:19.440 --> 09:20.910
When my mother was in Shangjing years ago,

09:20.910 --> 09:22.510
she heard from Empress Wenxi

09:22.710 --> 09:25.150
that the latter's brother
was originally a righteous man.

09:25.150 --> 09:27.240
But now this man has become
completely different.

09:27.240 --> 09:28.360
You don't think

09:28.600 --> 09:30.400
he'll easily surrender, right?

09:57.790 --> 09:59.790
My own design can't stump me, can it?

10:18.320 --> 10:20.800
Shao Yang, here I come.

10:23.670 --> 10:25.670
Your Highness, the mine collapsed.

10:25.820 --> 10:27.430
Yuan Xiaoliu is dead.

10:28.960 --> 10:29.560
Xiao Wuyi!

10:30.490 --> 10:31.290
Yuan Xiaoliu.

10:31.440 --> 10:31.910
Master.

10:32.110 --> 10:32.750
Wake up.

10:32.870 --> 10:33.670
Yuan Xiaoliu.

10:34.670 --> 10:35.470
Yuan Xiaoliu!

10:36.550 --> 10:37.320
Master!

10:38.510 --> 10:40.110
How exactly did this happen?

10:40.670 --> 10:42.030
It was my father's doing.

10:42.030 --> 10:44.360
He tried to drag everyone
to hell with him.

10:44.570 --> 10:46.150
All the polluted groundwater

10:46.150 --> 10:47.720
was kept beneath this mine.

10:48.630 --> 10:49.960
My father activated the mechanism

10:49.960 --> 10:53.090
so as to drown the entire Lingfeng Fort
with filthy water

10:53.270 --> 10:54.730
and take everyone's life.

11:18.910 --> 11:19.670
Xiao Wuyi!

11:19.950 --> 11:20.620
Xiao Wuyi!

11:21.320 --> 11:22.200
Xiao Wuyi!

11:22.600 --> 11:23.730
You cannot kill him.

11:24.270 --> 11:26.200
We must bring him back to Jiankang.

11:26.200 --> 11:28.390
That's the only way to expose
the Cui family's crimes to the world

11:28.390 --> 11:30.790
and truly avenge
those who died a wrongful death!

11:30.790 --> 11:32.360
This is how justice works!

11:59.160 --> 12:04.310
♪ The past is dust,
we're passing through ♪

12:05.530 --> 12:11.110
♪ No regrets for what we've lost and won ♪

12:11.770 --> 12:18.070
♪ The shape of time begins to fade ♪

12:18.340 --> 12:24.820
♪ Half by choice, half washed away ♪

12:25.230 --> 12:28.880
♪ Love and hate fade
like the shifting sand ♪

12:28.980 --> 12:31.430
♪ What's right or wrong is better
left unsaid ♪

12:31.600 --> 12:38.620
♪ As a mere traveller in the world,
do not ask about the cause and effect ♪

12:39.390 --> 12:41.750
Your master sacrificed his life
to save all of ours.

12:39.440 --> 12:42.510
[Tomb of Yuan Xiaoliu the Recluse]

12:49.320 --> 12:50.380
Princess Yunzhao,

12:50.600 --> 12:51.630
truth to be told,

12:51.870 --> 12:54.270
I'm here at the Grand Tutor's request.

12:55.320 --> 12:57.600
He knew you were likely in Lingfeng Fort,

12:58.080 --> 13:00.080
so he asked me to bring you a message.

13:00.150 --> 13:01.750
That is, The Xie family in Jiankang

13:01.750 --> 13:03.910
will always await your safe return.

13:03.910 --> 13:05.870
No need.
All ties between him and me are severed

13:05.870 --> 13:07.270
now that we are divorced.

13:10.120 --> 13:11.580
You are such a free spirit.

13:11.790 --> 13:12.790
How admirable.

13:13.200 --> 13:14.910
After the disastrous happening,

13:14.910 --> 13:16.270
I finally realized

13:16.670 --> 13:18.330
that the Phoenix Heart Tokens

13:18.670 --> 13:20.070
truly exist in the world.

13:21.720 --> 13:24.720
There has always been a saying
among people in recent years—

13:24.720 --> 13:28.320
"When the Phoenix Heart Tokens appear,
peace shall be restored in the world."

13:28.320 --> 13:29.080
I wonder if you...

13:29.080 --> 13:30.030
If the world could be changed

13:30.030 --> 13:31.320
by just a few tokens,

13:31.790 --> 13:34.850
why would Young Lord Xiao
bother to implement reforms?

13:35.550 --> 13:36.480
The Phoenix Heart Tokens

13:36.480 --> 13:38.000
are simply something that Empress Wenxi

13:38.000 --> 13:40.150
left behind for those around her
to remember her by.

13:40.150 --> 13:42.350
As for that rumored Crown Prince Wenxi,

13:42.390 --> 13:43.630
it's pure nonsense.

13:44.750 --> 13:46.000
That day in court,

13:46.440 --> 13:48.790
I made a lie out of it

13:49.120 --> 13:50.780
just to cause Cui Jun to panic.

13:51.120 --> 13:52.960
As a holder of a Phoenix Heart Token,

13:52.960 --> 13:54.750
you were also entrusted
with Ye's moving to the south

13:54.750 --> 13:55.930
and the task of aiding Crown Prince Wenxi.

13:55.930 --> 13:57.870
Crown Prince Wenxi died a long time ago.

13:57.870 --> 13:58.750
He didn't die!

14:01.360 --> 14:03.820
Empress Wenxi and I were
as close as sisters.

14:03.880 --> 14:05.790
If her son had really survived,

14:06.520 --> 14:08.030
I would love him dearly.

14:09.200 --> 14:10.600
How would I have never shown any care

14:10.600 --> 14:12.130
for him during these years?

14:16.760 --> 14:17.520
Good then.

14:17.790 --> 14:19.790
I was just worried about my brother.

14:20.120 --> 14:22.180
If Crown Prince Wenxi truly existed,

14:22.770 --> 14:25.650
what would become of my brother?

14:26.120 --> 14:28.120
Hearing what you said today,

14:28.330 --> 14:29.590
I'm finally relieved.

14:30.000 --> 14:30.910
I shall

14:31.900 --> 14:32.980
take my leave then.

14:45.680 --> 14:48.080
How did it go?
Did you intercept the letter?

14:50.030 --> 14:53.890
Did Princess Yunzhao mention
the whereabouts of Crown Prince Wenxi?

14:59.680 --> 15:02.810
Bring the nanny in Prince Qi's Mansion
back to Jiankang.

15:03.120 --> 15:04.030
Your brother

15:04.920 --> 15:07.110
is not of royal blood at all.

15:07.600 --> 15:10.260
Yunzhao has long suspected
Prince Qi's origin.

15:10.550 --> 15:12.410
The purpose of her trip to Guazhou

15:12.510 --> 15:15.370
is probably to use
the Phoenix Heart Token she holds

15:15.550 --> 15:17.600
to command the other token holders

15:18.000 --> 15:21.460
to assist the Li lineage
of the royal house in gaining the throne.

15:21.460 --> 15:24.390
This is bad. She plans to reveal
Mao's real identity.

15:38.550 --> 15:39.840
This is the map of Ye.

15:40.750 --> 15:41.840
Close your eyes.

15:42.240 --> 15:43.200
Throw a dart.

15:43.270 --> 15:45.200
We will go wherever it lands.

15:45.480 --> 15:46.720
No need to shut my eyes.

15:46.720 --> 15:48.120
I'll just throw the dart.

15:52.790 --> 15:55.420
There's a place called the Cloud Pavilion
on Lai Lake.

15:55.420 --> 15:56.820
Let's go to Lake Lai then.

16:06.960 --> 16:07.960
You don't like it?

16:09.440 --> 16:11.200
How about we will travel all the way south

16:11.200 --> 16:13.660
in quest of the best copper mine
in the world?

16:15.480 --> 16:16.150
Mother,

16:17.000 --> 16:18.200
actually, I...

16:19.480 --> 16:21.000
Never mind. It's nothing.

16:23.410 --> 16:25.890
So you don't like traveling with me.

16:26.960 --> 16:29.360
Where would you like to go then, Yaoyao?

16:37.130 --> 16:37.730
Oh, right.

16:38.600 --> 16:40.840
I just recalled another wonderful place,

16:40.840 --> 16:43.550
where you can find your favorite dish,
tofu steamed in lotus leaves.

16:43.550 --> 16:45.950
In midsummer,
you can take a boat out to sea.

16:46.320 --> 16:48.180
How about we venture off to the sea

16:48.440 --> 16:50.240
and watch the sunrise together?

16:55.750 --> 16:58.150
Mother, are you writing a letter
to Father?

16:58.630 --> 16:59.240
Yes.

17:00.750 --> 17:01.670
Some things,

17:01.910 --> 17:04.040
I think, are better explained clearly

17:04.349 --> 17:05.400
to your father.

17:05.920 --> 17:08.319
There is a problem
with Cui Jun's identity.

17:08.510 --> 17:11.140
So is with the wrongful convictions
of the An and Lu families

17:11.140 --> 17:12.400
years ago, I'm afraid.

17:12.750 --> 17:14.859
So you're not going back
to Jiankang, Mother?

17:14.859 --> 17:15.920
No. What about you?

17:15.920 --> 17:16.849
Are you planning

17:17.030 --> 17:19.430
to go to the Northern Border
with Xiao Wuyi?

17:19.790 --> 17:20.920
Mother, I'm not...

17:22.589 --> 17:24.030
I made a promise to my master.

17:24.030 --> 17:25.359
I must not break my word.

17:50.790 --> 17:51.480
Yaoyao,

17:52.170 --> 17:53.830
what do you think of Xiao Wuyi?

17:55.630 --> 17:57.290
Did you have a good time living

17:57.960 --> 17:59.620
in Prince Jing'an's Mansion?

18:05.960 --> 18:06.720
Mother.

18:10.070 --> 18:11.070
I think...

18:11.830 --> 18:14.400
he's somewhat different
from what people say about him.

18:14.400 --> 18:16.000
He's actually a great general.

18:16.000 --> 18:17.400
"Who says we stand alone?

18:18.070 --> 18:19.330
We share weal and woe."

18:19.640 --> 18:20.480
Indeed, he chose

18:20.480 --> 18:22.210
a rather good name for himself.

18:22.840 --> 18:25.640
But I was asking your opinion
about him as a person.

18:25.750 --> 18:26.510
He...

18:27.310 --> 18:29.350
could be quite annoying sometimes.

18:29.590 --> 18:32.510
But, I guess, maybe he can be

18:32.640 --> 18:34.040
considered a gentleman.

18:36.270 --> 18:38.920
Let bygones be bygones.

18:40.070 --> 18:42.640
Young Lord Xiao has agreed to let you go.

18:43.310 --> 18:44.550
Have you made any plans

18:44.550 --> 18:45.550
for your future?

18:46.830 --> 18:48.960
I'll travel the world with you
for sure, Mother.

18:48.960 --> 18:50.720
Haven't you already planned it all out?

18:50.720 --> 18:52.640
In the past, I was so immature

18:53.030 --> 18:54.560
that I often made you angry.

18:55.000 --> 18:56.960
From now on,
I will stick with you all the time.

18:56.960 --> 18:58.070
We shall never be apart.

18:58.070 --> 18:58.930
How about that?

19:10.250 --> 19:15.250
[Lingfeng Fort]

19:16.550 --> 19:17.880
You're leaving so soon?

19:19.270 --> 19:20.590
What happened at Lingfeng Fort
will be known.

19:20.590 --> 19:21.920
I'm afraid the Phoenix Heart Tokens

19:21.920 --> 19:23.480
will be coveted by many along the way.

19:23.480 --> 19:24.830
If I travel with you,

19:25.140 --> 19:26.400
there might be danger.

19:26.510 --> 19:29.170
So I'll take a different route
back to Jiankang.

19:33.550 --> 19:34.750
Will you...

19:35.160 --> 19:36.290
go back to my mansion

19:37.830 --> 19:38.560
in Jiankang?

19:40.920 --> 19:43.720
My mother and I will send Lejun back
to Jiankang first,

19:43.720 --> 19:46.120
and then head directly south
to Shu County.

19:46.590 --> 19:47.310
Shu County?

19:50.270 --> 19:51.350
Yes. My mother

19:51.370 --> 19:53.640
told me she once saw
crystal-clear pools there,

19:53.640 --> 19:55.720
so I'd like to go and see for myself.

20:00.390 --> 20:01.260
Then...

20:11.190 --> 20:12.590
Try not to get kidnapped.

20:17.110 --> 20:18.070
Don't worry.

20:19.090 --> 20:20.110
I'll continue the studies

20:20.110 --> 20:21.960
on my master's caltrop fireball.

20:21.960 --> 20:23.160
If anything comes up,

20:23.830 --> 20:25.490
I'll inform you immediately.

20:26.310 --> 20:26.830
Good.

20:28.830 --> 20:29.640
Well then...

20:30.510 --> 20:31.370
I'll get going.

20:33.140 --> 20:33.860
Sure.

20:57.030 --> 20:57.750
Li!

20:58.510 --> 20:59.270
Here you come.

20:59.270 --> 21:01.270
The usual, half salty and half sweet?

21:01.270 --> 21:01.950
Yes.

21:02.720 --> 21:03.240
Wait a moment.

21:03.240 --> 21:04.110
My wife

21:04.110 --> 21:05.530
loves the rice cake you make.

21:05.530 --> 21:06.720
After being away for days,

21:06.720 --> 21:08.060
I bet she misses this delicacy.

21:08.060 --> 21:10.070
How very lucky of your wife to have you,

21:10.070 --> 21:11.880
such a caring man, as her husband.

21:11.880 --> 21:12.880
Alright. Thanks.

21:13.040 --> 21:13.570
Goodbye.

21:17.640 --> 21:18.200
Master.

21:19.310 --> 21:20.910
A secret letter has arrived.

21:23.110 --> 21:25.960
I've found out the mysterious
Phoenix Heart Token is related to a mine.

21:25.960 --> 21:26.490
Besides,

21:26.640 --> 21:28.200
Princess Yunzhao and Cui Jun

21:28.200 --> 21:29.830
each hold a Phoenix Heart Token.

21:29.830 --> 21:30.960
The relationship between Xie Jiayu

21:30.960 --> 21:32.200
and Xiao Wuyi has changed.

21:32.200 --> 21:35.530
Princess Yunzhao will possibly
join forces with Xiao Wuyi.

21:36.250 --> 21:37.620
I'm ready to go all out.

21:39.550 --> 21:41.590
Why would she partner with Xiao Wuyi?

21:41.590 --> 21:43.110
T-That's impossible.

21:43.400 --> 21:44.840
Do not act rashly.

21:45.270 --> 21:47.640
We'll devise a plan
when you're back to Jiankang.

21:47.640 --> 21:50.160
Have this letter delivered
to Princess Pingning.

21:50.160 --> 21:51.560
Remember: make it quick.

21:52.510 --> 21:53.000
Yes.

22:10.780 --> 22:12.760
[Lingfeng Fort]

22:17.590 --> 22:18.790
Your Highness, Lady Xie,

22:18.790 --> 22:20.750
Young Lord Xiao ordered Qing Long and me
to escort you two.

22:20.750 --> 22:22.010
How thoughtful of him.

22:24.120 --> 22:25.120
Let's go, Mother.

22:29.460 --> 22:30.390
Anything wrong?

22:31.830 --> 22:33.720
Mother, I'm feeling a bit unwell.

22:34.030 --> 22:36.790
Yaoyao, after the incident
you just went through,

22:36.790 --> 22:38.850
I'm sure you need to lie down and rest.

22:39.640 --> 22:42.300
Why not ride with me instead,
Princess Yunzhao?

22:44.680 --> 22:45.440
It's a good idea.

22:45.440 --> 22:46.310
I'm fine, Mother.

22:46.310 --> 22:47.310
I have recovered.

22:47.440 --> 22:48.070
Maybe we should still...

22:48.070 --> 22:48.750
Yaoyao,

22:48.990 --> 22:50.510
please listen to Princess Yunzhao.

22:50.510 --> 22:51.920
If you get ill,

22:51.920 --> 22:53.650
everyone will be very worried.

22:57.680 --> 22:58.480
Be a good girl.

22:59.310 --> 23:00.350
Get some rest.

23:29.830 --> 23:30.510
My Lady,

23:30.880 --> 23:31.880
His Highness said

23:31.880 --> 23:33.610
you must not tire yourself out.

23:34.430 --> 23:36.240
Who on earth do you work for, me or him?

23:36.240 --> 23:37.920
As long as it's for
Your Ladyship's own good,

23:37.920 --> 23:38.920
I'll listen to it.

23:47.110 --> 23:49.550
I don't think Your Ladyship is rushing
to draft the caltrop fireball

23:49.550 --> 23:51.010
entirely for Master Yuan.

23:53.030 --> 23:54.360
The horse got startled!

23:55.710 --> 23:56.400
Oh no!

23:57.590 --> 23:58.680
Mother, Lejun!

24:08.110 --> 24:08.780
Mother!

24:13.960 --> 24:14.920
Mother!

24:15.050 --> 24:15.860
Mother!

24:24.130 --> 24:24.960
Mother!

24:28.710 --> 24:30.120
Xiao Wuyi, let go of me!

24:31.160 --> 24:32.110
Mother!

24:32.720 --> 24:34.160
Mother!

24:36.400 --> 24:38.350
Let go of me!

24:48.030 --> 24:49.480
Mother...

24:49.480 --> 24:50.270
Your Highness!

24:50.270 --> 24:52.600
-Princess Pingning!
-Princess Yunzhao!

24:52.880 --> 24:54.640
-Princess Yunzhao!
-Mother!

24:55.000 --> 24:56.130
Princess Pingning!

24:56.200 --> 24:57.260
Princess Yunzhao!

24:58.030 --> 25:00.030
-Princess Yunzhao!
-Princess Pingning!

25:00.030 --> 25:00.830
Mother...

25:00.830 --> 25:02.160
Princess Pingning!

25:02.790 --> 25:03.920
Princess Pingning!

25:04.030 --> 25:05.550
-Princess Pingning!
-Princess Yunzhao!

25:05.550 --> 25:07.030
Princess Yunzhao!

25:07.030 --> 25:08.720
-Mother!
-Princess Pingning!

25:08.720 --> 25:09.920
Princess Yunzhao!

25:10.030 --> 25:11.110
Mother...

25:11.750 --> 25:13.030
Princess Pingning!

25:13.440 --> 25:14.920
-Princess Yunzhao!
-Mother...

25:14.920 --> 25:16.650
-Princess Pingning!
-Mother!

25:17.030 --> 25:18.090
Princess Yunzhao!

25:19.430 --> 25:20.630
I found Her Highness!

25:57.440 --> 25:58.510
Mother...

25:59.540 --> 26:00.670
Mother!

26:02.070 --> 26:03.240
Mother!

26:05.680 --> 26:06.720
Mother...

26:08.440 --> 26:09.440
Mother...

26:12.300 --> 26:13.360
The daughter I want

26:13.770 --> 26:16.370
is not some puppet
who only knows how to obey me,

26:17.110 --> 26:18.070
but a young woman

26:18.280 --> 26:20.090
who truly knows what she wants

26:20.720 --> 26:22.720
and what she ought to do.

26:24.400 --> 26:27.330
Your parents are not the ones
you can truly depend on—

26:28.400 --> 26:29.750
only you are.

26:33.640 --> 26:35.070
Mother!

26:37.750 --> 26:38.790
Mother...

26:42.880 --> 26:44.070
Mother...

26:48.270 --> 26:50.330
Your Highness, the coachman is dead.

26:59.240 --> 27:00.070
Mother...

27:00.070 --> 27:01.440
What about Princess Pingning?

27:01.440 --> 27:02.270
Not found yet.

27:03.030 --> 27:04.230
Go on with the search.

27:04.550 --> 27:05.810
Make sure you find her,

27:06.350 --> 27:07.510
dead or alive.

27:07.840 --> 27:08.310
Yes.

27:11.360 --> 27:12.160
Mother...

27:14.400 --> 27:15.400
Mother...

27:32.350 --> 27:33.030
My Lady.

27:33.680 --> 27:35.810
these are Her Highness's belongings.

27:54.550 --> 27:55.960
Is anything missing?

28:01.610 --> 28:02.920
The Phoenix Heart Token...

28:02.920 --> 28:04.550
Could it have dropped somewhere
when Her Highness

28:04.550 --> 28:05.440
fell off the cliff?

28:05.440 --> 28:06.570
That's impossible.

28:07.000 --> 28:09.400
I saw Mother place it
right next to her skin.

28:14.020 --> 28:16.080
Is Your Ladyship suspecting
that someone murdered Her Highness

28:16.080 --> 28:17.680
in order to obtain the token?

28:17.830 --> 28:19.490
Before she fell off the cliff,

28:19.570 --> 28:21.700
that horse was clearly out of control.

28:22.750 --> 28:23.510
Mother!

28:26.080 --> 28:27.330
Go examine the forage

28:27.720 --> 28:28.980
and the dead coachman.

28:29.230 --> 28:29.750
Got it.

28:36.560 --> 28:38.030
We found Princess Pingning!

28:38.030 --> 28:39.290
We found Her Highness!

28:43.350 --> 28:44.610
Where did you find her?

28:44.880 --> 28:46.000
Your Highness was fortunately

28:46.000 --> 28:48.000
caught on a dead branch
right by the cliff.

28:48.000 --> 28:48.930
Injured though,

28:49.110 --> 28:50.560
Her Highness's life is not in danger.

28:50.560 --> 28:51.360
That's good.

28:56.720 --> 28:58.380
I investigated many a matter.

28:58.480 --> 29:00.200
This is roughly how the incident happened.

29:00.200 --> 29:01.260
The horse went wild

29:01.720 --> 29:02.920
because it ate the grains and forage

29:02.920 --> 29:04.780
contaminated by the dirty water.

29:05.110 --> 29:06.240
And all those grains and forage

29:06.240 --> 29:08.160
were already sealed by my order.

29:09.200 --> 29:11.310
I even specifically prepared
a horse carriage.

29:11.310 --> 29:14.310
Now the biggest suspect
of Princess Yunzhao's murder

29:14.440 --> 29:15.070
is me.

29:15.460 --> 29:16.460
It does appear so.

29:16.690 --> 29:18.400
But Lady Xie is very perceptive.

29:18.400 --> 29:19.860
The clearer the evidence
against Your Highness,

29:19.860 --> 29:21.590
the less likely Her Ladyship
is to suspect you.

29:21.590 --> 29:24.190
Whether she suspects me or not
doesn't matter.

29:24.440 --> 29:26.970
The point is, the deceased
is Jiayu's mother.

29:29.160 --> 29:30.560
Now, the more care I show,

29:30.940 --> 29:32.870
the messier the situation will be.

29:38.240 --> 29:38.830
My Lady!

29:40.830 --> 29:42.230
Are you alright, My Lady?

29:43.210 --> 29:43.860
Jiayu.

29:46.130 --> 29:47.130
She's burning up.

29:47.210 --> 29:48.540
Quick, go get Ruisheng!

29:55.070 --> 29:56.070
Xiao Wuyi.

29:58.350 --> 29:59.830
Before my mother's fall,

30:00.750 --> 30:02.110
had you seen her

30:02.620 --> 30:04.690
or heard her mention

30:05.440 --> 30:06.900
anyone trying to harm her?

30:09.620 --> 30:10.610
Does sitting in that chair

30:10.610 --> 30:12.740
mean all the constraints will go away?

30:13.370 --> 30:15.310
The military is controlled
by noble families.

30:15.310 --> 30:16.960
Whoever takes that post is bound to be

30:16.960 --> 30:18.360
subject to constraints.

30:18.440 --> 30:20.240
That's why I established Beifu,

30:20.880 --> 30:23.480
an army that doesn't
answer to noble families.

30:25.730 --> 30:26.250
No.

30:39.480 --> 30:40.240
Father...

30:44.350 --> 30:45.510
Mother...

30:48.350 --> 30:51.080
♪ One glance from near stirs my heart ♪

30:48.450 --> 30:49.540
Xiao Wuyi...

30:50.590 --> 30:51.240
I'm here.

30:51.300 --> 30:53.850
♪ This fleeting moment ♪

30:53.270 --> 30:54.160
Xie Jiayu,

30:55.110 --> 30:56.550
do you know who you are asking for?

30:55.550 --> 30:59.560
♪ Tugs the threads woven by fate ♪

30:59.730 --> 31:01.730
♪ Bound tight evermore ♪

31:03.690 --> 31:06.690
♪ Sharing all the years together ♪

31:05.350 --> 31:06.000
Jiayu

31:07.100 --> 31:11.470
♪ Peace I find nowhere but by your side ♪

31:08.310 --> 31:09.240
Don't be afraid.

31:12.060 --> 31:14.970
♪ Bear witness with our souls ♪

31:15.900 --> 31:18.720
♪ Fear no partings or wax and wane ♪

31:20.240 --> 31:24.570
♪ You know me and decided to
live and die together ♪

31:24.600 --> 31:28.250
♪ Believe in my persistence that
I won't run away ♪

31:28.280 --> 31:32.420
♪ You know I'm unyielding ♪

31:33.250 --> 31:36.170
♪ Don't give up or dodge ♪

31:36.760 --> 31:40.530
♪ You know me, seeing things
through from start to finish ♪

31:41.060 --> 31:45.170
♪ You see my move
under rebellious cover ♪

31:44.160 --> 31:45.020
Get some sleep.

31:45.440 --> 31:49.420
♪ You know me, I'm willing to be
with you till the end ♪

31:47.240 --> 31:48.900
Dawn will eventually arrive.

31:49.440 --> 31:53.380
♪ Burn the fire in my heart ♪

31:53.400 --> 31:57.610
♪ Sincere hearts remain as of old ♪

31:58.110 --> 32:00.030
Not all the toxins from the polluted water
were cleared from Jiayu's system.

32:00.030 --> 32:01.470
Neither did she have time
to rest properly.

32:01.470 --> 32:03.030
Then, Princess Yunzhao's death
hit her hard.

32:03.030 --> 32:05.240
She turned like this
due to emotional blows.

32:05.240 --> 32:06.590
The remaining toxins in her
must be purged.

32:06.590 --> 32:07.750
What medicinal materials are needed?

32:07.750 --> 32:08.830
I'll have Qing Long go buy them.

32:08.830 --> 32:10.030
I have all the common kinds,

32:10.030 --> 32:11.430
but a rare one is lacking—

32:12.070 --> 32:12.750
bear gall.

32:42.870 --> 32:44.350
My Lady, you're awake.

32:46.870 --> 32:48.110
How long was I asleep?

32:48.960 --> 32:49.750
Two days.

32:53.830 --> 32:54.680
What is this?

32:54.920 --> 32:56.070
It smells terrible.

32:56.200 --> 32:57.920
It's bear gall, a cure for toxins.

32:57.920 --> 32:59.070
Where did it come from?

32:59.070 --> 33:00.720
Probably provided by Madam Ruisheng.

33:00.720 --> 33:01.640
That treasure box of hers surely has

33:01.640 --> 33:03.970
all sorts of medicinal materials, right?

33:10.030 --> 33:12.070
The journey has been paused for too long.

33:12.070 --> 33:14.130
It's time we headed back to Jiankang.

33:20.920 --> 33:21.640
My Lady,

33:21.920 --> 33:23.680
Princess Yunzhao passed away so suddenly.

33:23.680 --> 33:26.210
How should we hold a funeral
for Her Highness?

33:26.510 --> 33:27.510
Theorectically,

33:27.830 --> 33:30.270
since Her Highness already divorced
the Grand Tutor,

33:30.270 --> 33:33.330
her coffin should be placed
in the Princess's Mansion.

33:33.400 --> 33:34.720
However, the princess's fief,

33:34.720 --> 33:36.780
namely Yun County, was conquered
by Northern Qin long ago.

33:36.780 --> 33:38.720
Her control over it was just nominal.

33:38.720 --> 33:40.000
Neither was her mansion

33:40.000 --> 33:41.600
ever relocated to Jiankang.

33:42.100 --> 33:44.230
Then where should we bring her coffin?

33:45.920 --> 33:47.580
To Prince Jing'an's Mansion?

33:49.200 --> 33:51.480
From now on,
I'll stick with you all the time.

33:51.480 --> 33:52.810
We shall never be apart.

33:56.550 --> 33:57.410
Your Highness!

33:58.200 --> 34:00.400
Prince Qi and the Grand Tutor have come.

34:25.250 --> 34:26.810
Yaoyao, where is Lejun?

34:27.570 --> 34:28.940
In the carriage behind.

34:29.510 --> 34:31.360
She fell off the cliff with my mother,

34:31.360 --> 34:33.760
and is still in a coma
with severe injuries.

34:39.290 --> 34:40.800
Bring her back to the palace now,

34:40.800 --> 34:42.460
and summon royal physicians!

34:46.960 --> 34:50.280
How did Princess Pingning

34:51.050 --> 34:53.940
and Yunzhao fall off the cliff together?

34:55.670 --> 34:56.320
Father,

34:57.480 --> 34:58.540
it was all my fault.

34:59.550 --> 35:02.030
I was supposed to share
a carriage with Lejun,

35:02.030 --> 35:03.400
but I felt unwell

35:03.650 --> 35:04.640
and needed to lie down,

35:04.640 --> 35:06.040
so we swapped carriages.

35:06.800 --> 35:08.600
Because the horse was startled,

35:08.790 --> 35:10.790
her carriage plunged off the cliff.

35:22.270 --> 35:22.910
Father,

35:24.550 --> 35:25.150
I...

35:26.510 --> 35:26.960
I...

35:40.760 --> 35:41.490
Grand Tutor,

35:42.000 --> 35:43.200
Jiayu didn't wish for

35:43.510 --> 35:45.040
Princess Yunzhao's death,

35:45.590 --> 35:47.790
nor does she have anything to do with it.

35:50.920 --> 35:53.050
How does it have nothing to do with her?

35:56.030 --> 35:58.630
Who told you to switch carriages
with Yunzhao?

35:59.140 --> 36:00.540
If it had never happened,

36:03.110 --> 36:04.770
it would've been you who died.

36:07.550 --> 36:09.680
It couldn't have been Yunzhao, right?

36:12.840 --> 36:15.400
Everyone of the Xie family, listen!

36:17.070 --> 36:20.190
Princess Yunzhao and I
simply adopted Xie Jiayu.

36:21.480 --> 36:23.710
She was not given birth by us.

36:26.230 --> 36:27.670
From now on,

36:29.230 --> 36:32.430
this woman is no longer
the daughter of the Xie family.

36:36.250 --> 36:37.560
She is not allowed

36:38.740 --> 36:40.940
to step into the Xie Mansion ever again.

36:46.880 --> 36:47.630
Guards!

36:48.070 --> 36:48.710
Yes.

36:51.250 --> 36:53.370
Escort the princess's coffin

36:54.650 --> 36:55.700
back home.

36:55.880 --> 36:56.630
Yes.

37:01.630 --> 37:03.440
On the genealogical record,

37:05.110 --> 37:06.760
I, Xie Huaigui, and Yunzhao,

37:08.330 --> 37:10.890
will remain as husband and wife forever.

37:13.360 --> 37:14.690
We were never divorced.

37:15.920 --> 37:17.070
Never.

37:19.230 --> 37:20.630
I'm taking my wife home.

37:22.670 --> 37:24.880
None of you can stop me.

37:25.280 --> 37:26.010
Grand Tutor!

37:40.110 --> 37:42.000
Xiao Wuyi, go back without me.

37:43.110 --> 37:44.070
I need a word

37:44.800 --> 37:45.880
with Mao.

37:58.490 --> 38:00.880
I didn't expect you to be involved
in the Cui Family Case.

38:00.880 --> 38:01.920
I was frightened upon receiving

38:01.920 --> 38:02.960
that letter from Lejun.

38:02.960 --> 38:04.290
Don't beat yourself up.

38:04.920 --> 38:06.910
What happened to Lejun
and Princess Yunzhao was an accident.

38:06.910 --> 38:08.110
It wasn't your fault.

38:10.670 --> 38:12.670
My mother didn't die of an accident.

38:13.760 --> 38:14.480
What?

38:14.880 --> 38:16.720
Her Phoenix Heart Token has gone missing.

38:16.720 --> 38:17.540
Someone must have

38:17.540 --> 38:19.230
murdered her for the token,

38:19.840 --> 38:21.900
and Lejun became collateral damage.

38:22.920 --> 38:24.320
Do the Phoenix Heart Tokens truly exist?

38:24.320 --> 38:26.360
Cui Jun and my mother each had one.

38:27.190 --> 38:28.960
If it hadn't been for these tokens,

38:28.960 --> 38:31.480
I wouldn't have been tricked into
going to Lingfeng Fort by Cui Jun.

38:31.480 --> 38:32.840
He originally intended to use me

38:32.840 --> 38:35.100
to force my mother to hand over her token.

38:35.400 --> 38:36.730
Yet he failed in the end.

38:38.880 --> 38:40.480
I find Xiao Wuyi suspicious.

38:42.190 --> 38:43.190
The horse went wild

38:43.190 --> 38:45.070
for eating the grains in Lingfeng Fort,

38:45.070 --> 38:47.360
which were polluted
by the dirty mine water.

38:47.360 --> 38:48.290
All those grains

38:48.480 --> 38:50.880
had been collected
and sealed by Xiao Wuyi.

38:51.230 --> 38:53.230
No one could access them except him.

38:54.760 --> 38:56.400
He already coveted the Cui family's mines

38:56.400 --> 38:57.710
back in Lingfeng Fort.

38:58.630 --> 39:00.230
So he's the biggest suspect.

39:01.840 --> 39:03.550
Lejun is severely injured
and in a coma now.

39:03.550 --> 39:04.950
When she comes to, please

39:05.010 --> 39:06.840
ask her to do me a favor
and think carefully

39:06.840 --> 39:08.900
if there is any other witness or clue.

39:09.620 --> 39:12.020
I've someone to find the coachman's family

39:12.550 --> 39:14.350
in the hope of gaining new clues.

39:14.480 --> 39:15.280
But, Yaoyao,

39:16.000 --> 39:17.550
if you're truly suspecting Wuyi,

39:17.550 --> 39:19.400
then you must not return to his mansion.

39:19.400 --> 39:21.030
If not, how am I supposed to find

39:21.030 --> 39:22.890
my mother's Phoenix Heart Token?

39:22.990 --> 39:24.800
This item is of great importance.

39:24.800 --> 39:27.060
He must have hidden it somewhere secret.

39:27.280 --> 39:28.610
Perhaps he has it on him.

39:29.840 --> 39:31.230
As long as I find this token,

39:31.230 --> 39:32.840
I'll be able to prove him
to be the murderer.

39:32.840 --> 39:33.480
Yaoyao...

39:33.550 --> 39:34.230
Mao.

39:37.880 --> 39:38.920
My mother is dead.

39:39.510 --> 39:41.880
The only person
who loved me unconditionally

39:41.880 --> 39:43.880
in this world died a wrongful death.

39:45.400 --> 39:47.400
I swear to find out the murderer,

39:48.550 --> 39:49.680
whoever that may be.

39:52.000 --> 39:54.330
I will make sure
justice is served for her.

39:59.890 --> 40:02.620
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

40:03.280 --> 40:04.410
Maybe Your Highness

40:04.440 --> 40:08.040
should have the bear-induced wounds
checked by the physicians.

40:13.920 --> 40:15.230
Have Cui Jun and Cui Shao'an

40:15.230 --> 40:16.280
been properly arranged?

40:16.280 --> 40:18.760
Yes, all is done
as per Your Highness's orders.

40:18.760 --> 40:21.070
What happened at Lingfeng Fort
will soon be known.

40:21.070 --> 40:23.610
With two Phoenix Heart Tokens
appearing at once,

40:23.610 --> 40:25.220
anyone would be tempted.

40:26.400 --> 40:27.320
I'd like to see

40:28.400 --> 40:29.880
who will show up for them.

40:30.280 --> 40:31.840
Xiao Wuyi, I'm back.

40:55.920 --> 40:57.850
You finished that talk with Yizhi?

40:59.190 --> 41:01.720
Yes, I was giving him some advice
about Lejun.

41:06.230 --> 41:07.630
Are you explaining to me?

41:16.760 --> 41:18.360
I'd like to have a clean room.

41:19.030 --> 41:21.070
Wensheng Courtyard has always been yours.

41:21.070 --> 41:22.930
I want to set up a memorial tablet.

41:23.840 --> 41:25.100
Before my mother died,

41:25.400 --> 41:27.240
she had decided to divorce that man.

41:27.240 --> 41:28.710
I'm afraid her spirit in heaven

41:28.710 --> 41:30.670
would hate to return
to the Grand Tutor's Mansion.

41:30.670 --> 41:31.710
So, I plan to set up a memorial tablet

41:31.710 --> 41:32.840
for her in Wensheng Yard.

41:32.840 --> 41:34.440
This way, I can mourn for her.

41:36.480 --> 41:37.190
As I said,

41:37.840 --> 41:39.800
Wensheng Yard has always been yours.

41:39.800 --> 41:41.400
Feel free to make your own decision.

41:41.400 --> 41:42.030
Got it.

41:55.030 --> 41:55.670
Lejun,

41:57.110 --> 41:58.670
the imperial physician said

41:58.670 --> 42:01.130
you hit your head
when you fell off the cliff.

42:01.760 --> 42:03.560
That's why you've been in a coma.

42:04.030 --> 42:06.090
Are you going to stay asleep like this

42:06.280 --> 42:07.920
and never wake up again?

42:09.030 --> 42:10.290
What exactly happened

42:10.960 --> 42:12.110
in the carriage?

42:19.690 --> 42:20.730
Yaoyao said

42:21.890 --> 42:25.670
Xiao Wuyi murdered Princess Yunzhao
to get her Phoenix Heart Token.

42:25.670 --> 42:26.440
She has also sent people

42:26.440 --> 42:28.170
to find the coachman's family.

42:28.750 --> 42:30.210
Though the latter is dead,

42:30.590 --> 42:32.050
his family might have seen

42:32.280 --> 42:33.760
who replaced the forage

42:33.760 --> 42:35.220
with the polluted grains.

42:36.030 --> 42:37.920
As long as the witnesses
arrive in Jiankang,

42:37.920 --> 42:39.330
they can immediately testify

42:39.330 --> 42:41.860
who exactly harmed you
and Princess Yunzhao.

42:45.690 --> 42:48.490
Li Lejun, you're actually conscious,
aren't you?

42:48.690 --> 42:50.820
Are you sure you want to keep up the act?

42:55.790 --> 42:56.750
Mao.

43:01.870 --> 43:02.800
Are you alright?

43:02.920 --> 43:04.280
Have Yaoyao and her people really found

43:04.280 --> 43:05.360
the coachman's family?

43:05.360 --> 43:07.550
Did they truly see
who tempered with the forage?

43:07.550 --> 43:08.030
No...

43:09.360 --> 43:10.560
It can't be possible.

43:11.000 --> 43:12.130
So it really was you.

43:21.150 --> 43:22.550
Please punish me, Mao.

43:23.400 --> 43:24.800
Why on earth did you do it?

43:24.840 --> 43:26.970
This matter has nothing to do with you.

43:27.000 --> 43:29.110
It's better for you not to know the truth.

43:29.110 --> 43:30.550
You caused Princess Yunzhao's death,

43:30.550 --> 43:32.080
and framed Xiao Wuyi for it.

43:32.150 --> 43:33.840
Xiao Wuyi is not someone
to be trifled with.

43:33.840 --> 43:34.800
Tell the truth already.

43:34.800 --> 43:35.960
If not, what are you going to do

43:35.960 --> 43:37.320
when he starts investigating it?

43:37.320 --> 43:37.850
Speak up.

43:38.360 --> 43:39.550
Prior your trip to Guazhou,

43:39.550 --> 43:41.320
what exactly did you
plot with the Grand Tutor?

43:41.320 --> 43:43.150
Why did you murder Princess Yunzhao?

43:43.150 --> 43:45.320
Because she had a Phoenix Heart Token.

43:46.510 --> 43:48.910
Because Crown Prince Wenxi is still alive.

43:49.150 --> 43:50.290
And more importantly,

43:50.290 --> 43:52.950
Princess Yunzhao knew
that you, my brother, are

43:55.340 --> 43:56.940
the Grand Tutor's son.

43:57.170 --> 43:58.090
What?
